Package: denoiseTDA
Type: Package
Title: De-noising for Topological Data Analysis
Version: 1.0
Date: 2019-08-09
Author: Uriya Jankurazova
Maintainer: Uriya Jankurazova <uriya.jan@outlook.com>
Description: "This package contains two algorithms, Kloke's algorithm (1) and mean shift algorithm (2), which de-noise data for further topological data analysis. \\ Reference \\ (1) Kloke, J. N., Carlsson, G., Kerckhoff, S., Mazzeo, R. (2010). Methods and applications of topological data analysis. Stanford University.\\ (2) Fukunaga, K., & Hostetler, L.D. (1975). The estimation of the gradient of a density function, with applications in pattern recognition. IEEE Trans. Inf. Theory, 21, 32-40."
